data.description: Unique 4BR/2.5BA home with mountain-esque charm! Sturdy log cabin with large fireplace in the family room, open concept dining, gunite pool in the fenced backyard, and two screened porches (front and back)! Bamboo flooring in the kitchen, gas range, and a large center island. This home has been well loved by its second owner for many years and is now ready for the third to add their own personal touch with updates. Handicap accessible home with a stair lift. Very close to the main entrance in a gated community. Take a look today!
